{"tid":2395072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警員睇錯燈撞死的士司機　06年判罰$8000","createTime":"2021-02-04T15:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T17:16:55.000Z","uid":36494,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7f8ebd5f2ce735679c6d8f2e0dd9bfa1ac32e2f2","tid":2395072,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:46:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20150628/EGKCLB7AHC6GZ5WODN5TIMJU4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20150628%2FEGKCLB7AHC6GZ5WODN5TIMJU4A%2F&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=fac2961a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20150628%2FEGKCLB7AHC6GZ5WODN5TIMJU4A%2F&h=85a7b3af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20150628/EGKCLB7AHC6GZ5WODN5TIMJU4A/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2006年前有警員趕查案「睇錯」交通燈，駕駛的衝鋒車在路口衝燈，攔腰撞向的士，的士司機重傷不治。該警員被控危險駕駛引致他人死亡罪，2006年的今日，獲判罰款8,000元及停牌6個月。"},{"pid":"bf97811ee4618b0d43557dab9cfd7f45e83cc840","tid":2395072,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:47:41.000Z","msg":"裁判官在荃灣法院宣判時，指被告聲稱看錯燈號，法庭有所保留，但認為被告一心趕往拯救他人生命，並非故意罔顧其他道路使用者的安全，考慮到被告過往有良好紀錄，故輕判他罰款8000元及停牌6個月。"},{"pid":"51a1201f5d290c4e727207e8b18206277c44c649","tid":2395072,"uid":43493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:48:34.000Z","msg":"dc9條命只值8000......<br />\nCLS"},{"pid":"2774276a7e29d3eca4a0a6e611d760dc727fc126","tid":2395072,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51a1201f5d290c4e727207e8b18206277c44c649","tid":2395072,"uid":43493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:48:34.000Z","msg":"dc9條命只值8000......<br />\nCLS"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:51:48.000Z","msg":"而家趕住用國安法拉人<br />\n直頭乜都唔駛罰添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33af051698ddd1f946c1734f22d3cd92816868ce","tid":2395072,"uid":106604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:53:07.000Z","msg":"花廳都唔洗坐下..."},{"pid":"f1dea365a301439263195135636b2cf3ce9281e1","tid":2395072,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"2006年6月28日，肇事車長在庭上承認危險駕駛引致他人死亡罪。其律師求情時指，被告任職警隊22年，<span class=\"red\">本身並非專門負責駕駛警車，但為「自我增值」，2000年考獲警車駕駛執照；肇事當晚也是臨時頂替因肚痛如廁而來不及出車的司機駕車</span>"},{"pid":"7b65c50e58bb67a477fb4c33f26329270d75f9f1","tid":2395072,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:07:38.000Z","msg":"邊隻官審？"},{"pid":"2b5e8ca267a9894fb546a96752e5153b63ee4214","tid":2395072,"uid":35440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f1dea365a301439263195135636b2cf3ce9281e1","tid":2395072,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"2006年6月28日，肇事車長在庭上承認危險駕駛引致他人死亡罪。其律師求情時指，被告任職警隊22年，<span class=\"red\">本身並非專門負責駕駛警車，但為「自我增值」，2000年考獲警車駕駛執照；肇事當晚也是臨時頂替因肚痛如廁而來不及出車的司機駕車</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:07:53.000Z","msg":"佢同事係鄭中基?"},{"pid":"8d99af13957e252ab959af0516f8670f65db7092","tid":2395072,"uid":380450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:14:24.000Z","msg":"可唔可以拎泥做案例"},{"pid":"42c342d2a0238809e8e0e7393875f4795b915a2e","tid":2395072,"uid":355499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"律政屍唔上訴既?"}]}